Usage: setObjFPlanBoxList [-help] {Cell Group Instance Layershape Module}
                          <objectName> <boxList> [-no_snap_to_grid]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
{Cell Group Instance Layershape Module}    # Object type (enum, required)
<objectName>           # Object name (string, required)
<boxList>              # rectilinear shape of an object (list, required)
-no_snap_to_grid       # Specify to not honor snap rules (bool, optional)